
    - By using Angular4 we can develop web applications and
      mobile applications.

    - we can develop angular4 applications by using "TypeScript".


Steps to Create the Angular4 Applications:
------------------------------------------

> npm install -g @angular/cli

> ng new demoapp

> cd demoapp

> ng serve

[Note : angular4 application by default running on "lite"
        server with the port no.4200]









